{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/iOS/220726-swift-struct-class/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Woody","author":"Woody","siteUrl":"https://gintooooonic.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"gintooooonic/gintooooonic.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"e67b2a43-a0e1-5b69-b93d-9761166bfdb1","excerpt":"Swift의 구조체와 클래스가 갖는\n공통점과 차이점에 대해 정리합니다. 1. 구조체와 클래스의 공통점 a. 프로퍼티와 메서드를 갖습니다. 구조체와 클래스 모두 데이터를 프로퍼티에 저장하고,\n동작을 메서드에 정의한다는 점이 같습니다. b. Initializer 메서드를 호출합니다. 인스턴스 생성 시 초기 상태를 설정하기 위해 Initializer 메서드를 호출합니다. c. extension 문법을 사용해 기능을 확장할 수 있습니다. 구조체나 클래스에 대한 extension…","html":"<p>Swift의 구조체와 클래스가 갖는\n공통점과 차이점에 대해 정리합니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-구조체와-클래스의-공통점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0%EC%B2%B4%EC%99%80-%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4%EC%9D%98-%EA%B3%B5%ED%86%B5%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"1 구조체와 클래스의 공통점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 구조체와 클래스의 공통점</h2>\n<h3 id=\"a-프로퍼티와-메서드를-갖습니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#a-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%ED%8D%BC%ED%8B%B0%EC%99%80-%EB%A9%94%EC%84%9C%EB%93%9C%EB%A5%BC-%EA%B0%96%EC%8A%B5%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"a 프로퍼티와 메서드를 갖습니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>a. 프로퍼티와 메서드를 갖습니다.</h3>\n<p>구조체와 클래스 모두 데이터를 프로퍼티에 저장하고,\n동작을 메서드에 정의한다는 점이 같습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// Property</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> age<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// Method</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">sayHi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">\\(</span><span class=\"token interpolation\">name</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token string\"> says hi.\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> person <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"Elon Musk\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> age<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">51</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>person<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// prints \"Elon Musk\"</span>\nperson<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sayHi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// prints \"Elon Musk says hi.\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"b-initializer-메서드를-호출합니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#b-initializer-%EB%A9%94%EC%84%9C%EB%93%9C%EB%A5%BC-%ED%98%B8%EC%B6%9C%ED%95%A9%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"b initializer 메서드를 호출합니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>b. Initializer 메서드를 호출합니다.</h3>\n<p>인스턴스 생성 시 초기 상태를 설정하기 위해 Initializer 메서드를 호출합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> age<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> age<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> name\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>age <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> age\n\t\t<span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"name: </span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">\\(</span><span class=\"token interpolation\">name</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token string\">, age: </span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">\\(</span><span class=\"token interpolation\">age</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token string\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// prints \"name: Elon Musk, age: 51\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> person <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"Elon Musk\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> age<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">51</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"c-extension-문법을-사용해-기능을-확장할-수-있습니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#c-extension-%EB%AC%B8%EB%B2%95%EC%9D%84-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%B4-%EA%B8%B0%EB%8A%A5%EC%9D%84-%ED%99%95%EC%9E%A5%ED%95%A0-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EC%8A%B5%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"c extension 문법을 사용해 기능을 확장할 수 있습니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>c. extension 문법을 사용해 기능을 확장할 수 있습니다.</h3>\n<p>구조체나 클래스에 대한 extension을 작성할 수 있습니다.\n예를 들면, 기본 타입인 <code class=\"language-text\">Int</code>도 구조체이기 때문에 아래처럼 제곱수를 반환하는 메서드를 추가해 사용할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">extension</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">square</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-></span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">self</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">self</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> num<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>num<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">square</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"d-protocol을-따를-수-있습니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#d-protocol%EC%9D%84-%EB%94%B0%EB%A5%BC-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EC%8A%B5%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"d protocol을 따를 수 있습니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>d. protocol을 따를 수 있습니다.</h3>\n<p>아래처럼 특정 프로토콜을 따를 수 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">protocol</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Talkable</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> message<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">get</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">set</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">say</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Talkable</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> message<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">say</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">\\(</span><span class=\"token interpolation\">name</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token string\"> says </span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">\\(</span><span class=\"token interpolation\">message</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token string\">.\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> person <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"Elon Musk\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> message<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"hello world\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nperson<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">say</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// prints \"Elon Musk says hello world.\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"2-구조체와-클래스의-차이점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0%EC%B2%B4%EC%99%80-%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4%EC%9D%98-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"2 구조체와 클래스의 차이점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 구조체와 클래스의 차이점</h2>\n<h3 id=\"a-상속\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#a-%EC%83%81%EC%86%8D\" aria-label=\"a 상속 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>a. 상속</h3>\n<p>객체지향 프로그래밍 경험에서 알고 있듯이,\n상속은 클래스가 갖고 있는 기능입니다.\n<strong>구조체는 상속할 수 없습니다.</strong></p>\n<p>더불어 클래스는 <strong>조상과 자손 타입간의 캐스팅</strong>이 가능합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> message<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> message<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> name\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>message <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> message\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Student</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> studentId<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> message<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> studentId<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>studentId <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> studentId\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> message<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> message<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> student <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Student</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"Elon Musk\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> message<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"hello world\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> studentId<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// type casting</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> person<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> student\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> std<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Student</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> person <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Student</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// downcast</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"b-값의-복사와-참조\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#b-%EA%B0%92%EC%9D%98-%EB%B3%B5%EC%82%AC%EC%99%80-%EC%B0%B8%EC%A1%B0\" aria-label=\"b 값의 복사와 참조 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>b. 값의 복사와 참조</h3>\n<p>기본적으로 구조체는 값 타입, 클래스는 참조 타입입니다.</p>\n<p>구조체의 인스턴스는 <strong>값의 복사를 통해 전달</strong>됩니다.\nStack 메모리에는 같은 값을 갖는 두 개의 서로 다른 변수가 존재하게 됩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">sayHi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">\\(</span><span class=\"token interpolation\">name</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token string\"> says hi.\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"Jake\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> a\na<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"Paul\"</span></span>\n\na<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sayHi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// prints \"Paul says hi.\"</span>\nb<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sayHi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// prints \"Jake says hi.\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>클래스의 인스턴스는 Heap 메모리에 존재하며,\n전달하고자 할 경우 <strong>메모리 공간에 대한 참조가 전달</strong>됩니다.\n여러 개의 변수가 하나의 Heap 메모리 공간을 가리킵니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> name\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">sayHi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">\\(</span><span class=\"token interpolation\">name</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token string\"> says hi.\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"Jake\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> a\na<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"Paul\"</span></span>\n\na<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sayHi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// prints \"Paul says hi.\"</span>\nb<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sayHi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// prints \"Paul says hi.\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"c-initializer와-deinitializer\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#c-initializer%EC%99%80-deinitializer\" aria-label=\"c initializer와 deinitializer permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>c. Initializer와 Deinitializer</h3>\n<p>구조체는 자동으로 Initializer 메서드를 생성해주지만,\n클래스는 그렇지 않습니다. 직접 <code class=\"language-text\">init()</code> 메서드를 정의해야 합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token comment\">// error: class 'Person' has no initializers</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>그리고 클래스는 Deinitializer를 정의할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> name\n\t\t<span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"Hi, I'm </span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">\\(</span><span class=\"token interpolation\">name</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token string\">.\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">deinit</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"I'm leaving!\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> person<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"Jake\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// prints \"Hi, I'm Jake.\"</span>\nperson <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token nil constant\">nil</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// prints \"I'm leaving!\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.swift.org/swift-book/LanguageGuide/ClassesAndStructures.html\">Structures and Classes — The Swift Programming Language (Swift 5.7)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.yagom.net/530/\">Swift - 구조체 클래스 - yagom’s blog</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/iOS/220726-swift-struct-class/#1-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0%EC%B2%B4%EC%99%80-%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4%EC%9D%98-%EA%B3%B5%ED%86%B5%EC%A0%90\">1. 구조체와 클래스의 공통점</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/iOS/220726-swift-struct-class/#a-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%ED%8D%BC%ED%8B%B0%EC%99%80-%EB%A9%94%EC%84%9C%EB%93%9C%EB%A5%BC-%EA%B0%96%EC%8A%B5%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\">a. 프로퍼티와 메서드를 갖습니다.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/iOS/220726-swift-struct-class/#b-initializer-%EB%A9%94%EC%84%9C%EB%93%9C%EB%A5%BC-%ED%98%B8%EC%B6%9C%ED%95%A9%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\">b. Initializer 메서드를 호출합니다.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/iOS/220726-swift-struct-class/#c-extension-%EB%AC%B8%EB%B2%95%EC%9D%84-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%B4-%EA%B8%B0%EB%8A%A5%EC%9D%84-%ED%99%95%EC%9E%A5%ED%95%A0-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EC%8A%B5%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\">c. extension 문법을 사용해 기능을 확장할 수 있습니다.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/iOS/220726-swift-struct-class/#d-protocol%EC%9D%84-%EB%94%B0%EB%A5%BC-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EC%8A%B5%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\">d. protocol을 따를 수 있습니다.</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/iOS/220726-swift-struct-class/#2-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0%EC%B2%B4%EC%99%80-%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4%EC%9D%98-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90\">2. 구조체와 클래스의 차이점</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/iOS/220726-swift-struct-class/#a-%EC%83%81%EC%86%8D\">a. 상속</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/iOS/220726-swift-struct-class/#b-%EA%B0%92%EC%9D%98-%EB%B3%B5%EC%82%AC%EC%99%80-%EC%B0%B8%EC%A1%B0\">b. 값의 복사와 참조</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/iOS/220726-swift-struct-class/#c-initializer%EC%99%80-deinitializer\">c. Initializer와 Deinitializer</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/iOS/220726-swift-struct-class/#reference\">Reference</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Swift의 구조체와 클래스","date":"July 26, 2022"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/iOS/220726-swift-struct-class/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/iOS/220723-ios-architecture-patterns/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"MVVM 아키텍처 패턴"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/iOS/220729-swiftui-state/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"SwiftUI의 @State와 @Binding"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2486386679","3128451518"]}